---
---

<section class="roadmap section reveal" id="roadmap">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="roadmap-header reveal delay-100">
      <div class="badge glow-badge" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">
        <span class="badge-text">Vision 2026</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title">The Future of <span class="accent-text">Automated Pharmacovigilance.</span></h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Gemmra is the beginning. These capabilities are on our research roadmap.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="roadmap-grid">
      <!-- Roadmap Item 1 -->
      <div class="roadmap-card reveal delay-200">
        <div class="roadmap-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="accent-icon"><path d="M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 17H20"></path><path d="M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>MedDRA Dictionary Augmentation</h3>
        <p>License the full MedDRA dictionary to expand PT coverage beyond BioDEX-derived terms. Add retrieval-augmented generation for real-time PT lookup during inference.</p>
        <span class="status-label">T2 Improvement</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Roadmap Item 2 -->
      <div class="roadmap-card reveal delay-300">
        <div class="roadmap-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="accent-icon"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Multi-Source Signal Detection</h3>
        <p>Aggregate case-level assessments into population-level safety signals. Cross-reference FDA FAERS, EMA EudraVigilance, and PMDA databases.</p>
        <span class="status-label">Population Safety</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Roadmap Item 3 -->
      <div class="roadmap-card reveal delay-400">
        <div class="roadmap-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="accent-icon"><path d="M18 10h-1.26A8 8 0 1 0 9 20h9a5 5 0 0 0 0-10z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Real-Time PV-as-a-Service</h3>
        <p>Production API with streaming thinking traces. Confidence-calibrated outputs with uncertainty estimation. Real-time monitoring dashboard.</p>
        <span class="status-label">Production Deployment</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .roadmap {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .roadmap::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border-accent), transparent);
  }

  .roadmap-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-4xl) auto;
  }

  .roadmap-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .roadmap-card {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-card);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    position: relative;
    transition: transform var(--transition-base), box-shadow var(--transition-base);
  }

  .roadmap-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 196, 204, 0.05);
    border-color: rgba(0, 196, 204, 0.3);
  }

  .roadmap-icon {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: rgba(0, 196, 204, 0.05);
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 196, 204, 0.2);
  }

  .roadmap-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--text-heading);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .roadmap-card p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .status-label {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    background: var(--bg-tertiary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .roadmap-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
